PLANT SAFETY OFFICER INSPECTION & HSE PROTOCOL GUIDE
Document Ref: SAF-2026-001 | Target Role: Safety Officers & HSE Leads

1. SAFETY OFFICER RESPONSIBILITIES IN INTELLIPLANT AI
- Receive automated real-time notifications whenever compliance inspections are completed by Maintenance Engineers (including delay reasons for overdue items).
- Monitor plant safety framework scores (ISO 45001, OISD, PESO, Factory Act).
- Maintain and renew machine operating permits, safety licenses (LIC-001 to LIC-006), and plant insurance policies (INS-001 to INS-006).
- Conduct monthly emergency response & LOTO safety drills.